results.name: a(n) = A051707(A025487).
comment: Number of factorizations of (n,n) into pairs (j,k) by prime signature.
Pairs (j,k) must satisfy j>1, k>=1; (a,b)*(x,y)=(a*x,b*y); unit is (1,1).
results.author: _Christian G. Bower_, Jun 03 2005
